10 An act relating to prohibiting possession of firearms and dangerous
11 weapons in State buildings and on State land
12 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
13 Sec. 1. 13 V.S.A. § 4028 is added to read
14 § 4028. POSSESSION OF FIREARMS AND DANGEROUS WEAPONS IN
15 STATE BUILDINGS AND ON STATE LAND PROHIBITED
16 (a) A person shall not knowingly possess a firearm or dangerous weapon in
17 a State building or on State land.
18 (b)(1) A person who violates subsection (a) of this section shall be
19 imprisoned for not more than one year or fined not more than $2,000.00, or
20 both.
